{"word":"G3579 - ξενίζω - xenízō - xen-id'-zo - Entertain","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ξενίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>xenízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>xen-id'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Entertain"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தங்கியிரு, உபசாரஞ்செய், உபசரி, நூதனம், ஆச்சரியப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to receive as a guest, to entertain hospitably"},{"paragraph":"2. to surprise or astonish by the strangeness and novelty of a thing"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3581 - ξένος - xénos - xen'-os/3581\">G3581</a>; to <i>be a host</i> (passively a <i>guest</i>); by implication <i>be</i> (<i>make</i>, <i>appear</i>) <i>strange:</i> - entertain, lodge, (think it) strange."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3578 - ξενία - xenía - xen-ee'-ah/3578\">G3578</a>, <a href=\"#/G3579 - ξενίζω - xenízō - xen-id'-zo/3579\">G3579</a>, <a href=\"#/G3580 - ξενοδοχέω - xenodochéō - xen-od-okh-eh'-o/3580\">G3580</a>, <a href=\"#/G3581 - ξένος - xénos - xen'-os/3581\">G3581</a>, <a href=\"#/G5381 - φιλονεξία - philonexía - fil-on-ex-ee'-ah/5381\">G5381</a>, <a href=\"#/G5382 - φιλόξενος - philóxenos - fil-ox'-en-os/5382\">G5382</a>"}]}